  The[0m[2m simulation[0m[2m confirms[0m[2m:[0m[2m
     
     -[0m[2m **Ghost[0m[2m charges**:[0m[2m 8[0m[2m orders were[0m[2m charged ([0m[2mtotal $[0m[2m800)[0m[2m but only[0m[2m 5[0m[2m succeeded.[0m[2m 3 orders[0m[2m paid[0m[2m then[0m[2m hit[0m[2m “[0m[2minventory error[0m[2m after payment[0m[2m”.[0m[2m
     - **[0m[2mOvers[0m[2melling potential[0m[2m**: `[0m[2mcheck_stock[0m[2m` and[0m[2m `de[0m[2mcrement`[0m[2m are separate[0m[2m,[0m[2m un[0m[2mprotected[0m[2m ops[0m[2m; concurrent[0m[2m orders[0m[2m can all[0m[2m pass[0m[2m the check[0m[2m before any[0m[2m decrement runs[0m[2m,[0m[2m driving[0m[2m stock[0m[2m negative.[0m[2m
     
     Root[0m[2m causes[0m[2m are[0m[2m clear[0m[2m. I'll[0m[2m apply[0m[2m the[0m[2m fix:[0m[2m
     
     1.[0m[2m **`[0m[2mInventory`[0m[2m**: add[0m[2m an `[0m[2masyncio[0m[2m.Lock`-[0m[2mprotected[0m[2m `reserve[0m[2m(quantity[0m[2m)` method[0m[2m that atom[0m[2mically checks[0m[2m +[0m[2m decrements[0m[2m. Also[0m[2m lock `[0m[2mincrement`[0m[2m/`[0m[2mdecrement[0m[2m` so[0m[2m rollback[0m[2m is safe[0m[2m.
     2[0m[2m. **`[0m[2mPaymentGateway[0m[2m`**:[0m[2m add an[0m[2m `async[0m[2mio.Lock[0m[2m` and[0m[2m a set[0m[2m of already[0m[2m-charged[0m[2m order IDs[0m[2m inside[0m[2m `charge[0m[2m`[0m[2m to guarantee[0m[2m idempot[0m[2mency and[0m[2m atomic[0m[2m bookkeeping[0m[2m.
     3[0m[2m. **`[0m[2mcheckout`[0m[2m**: reserve[0m[2m stock[0m[2m **first[0m[2m**, then[0m[2m charge.[0m[2m If payment[0m[2m fails,[0m[2m rollback[0m[2m the reservation[0m[2m. This[0m[2m eliminates[0m[2m the ghost[0m[2m-ch[0m[2marge window[0m[2m.[0m[2m
